Ward {2}
Whenever Alrund, the Wise enters the battlefield or attacks, scry 2. Then, exile the top card of your library face-down and look at it. It becomes foretold. Its foretell cost is its mana cost reduced by {2}.
Whenever you cast a spell from exile, create a 1/1 blue Bird creature token with flying.

Equipped creature has reach, deathtouch and “{2}, {T}: Investigate”. [i](To investigate, create a Clue token. It's an artifact with “{2}, Sacrifice this token: Draw a card.”)[/i]
Whenever you investigate, equipped creature deals 1 damage to any target.
Equip {2}

When Gornisari, the Arisen enters the battlefield, if you cast it from your hand, put two stun counter on each of up to two target permanents. [i](If a permanent with stun counters would untap, remove one instead.)[/i]
Vigilance, ward {4}
Whenever Gornisari attacks, defending player may put a permanent they both control and own on top of their library. If they don't, Gornisari can't be blocked this turn.

Flash, ward {4}
Projection Prodigy can't block.
If a copy of a spell would resolve or a token that's copy of a permanent would enter the battlefield, if it isn't a copy of Projection Prodigy, you may have the controller of that spell or permanent create that many tokens that are a copy of Projection Prodigy instead.

Kicker {G}
Whenever Insectoid Botanist enters the battlefield, if it was kicked, you may search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
[i]Landfall[/i] — Whenever a land enters the battlefield under your control, if this is the first time this ability has resolved this turn, create a 0/1 green Plant creature token. Otherwise, put a +1/+1 counter on target creature.

When Sword of the Dusk Clerics enters the battlefield, amass Clerics 2. Attach Sword of the Dusk Clerics to target Army. [i](To amass Clerics 2, put two +1/+1 counters on an Army you control. It's also a Cleric. If you don't control an Army, create a 0/0 black Cleric Army creature token first.)[/i]
Equipped creature has lifelink.
Equip {2}{B}

Decompose into Food {1}{G} [i]({1}{G}, Exile this card from your graveyard: Create a token that's a copy of it except it's a colorless Food artifact with no mana cost and “{2}, {T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Gain 3 life” and it loses all other card types. Decompose only as a sorcery)[/i]
Decompose into Clue {1}{U}
Decompose into Treasure {U}{G}
